### Naming Convention
- `get*` - Veri getir
- `create*` - Yeni kayıt oluştur
- `update*` - Güncelle
- `delete*` - Sil
- `calculate*` - Hesapla (örn: `calculateSimilarity`)

## 🗄️ Database Queries
```javascript
import Database from 'better-sqlite3'

const db = new Database('./data/quran.db')

// Prepared statements
const stmt = db.prepare('SELECT * FROM ayetler WHERE sure = ? AND ayet = ?')
const result = stmt.get(sure, ayet)
```

## ⚡ Performance Tips
- Prepared statements kullan (SQL injection'dan güvenli)
- Connection pooling (bir tane global DB instance)
- Caching layer (Redis veya in-memory)

## 🔐 Security
- Input validation (sure, ayet ranges)
- CORS ayarla
- Rate limiting (gelecek feature)
- SQL injection'dan koru (prepared statements)

## 📝 Error Handling
```javascript
router.use((err, req, res, next) => {
  console.error('[ERROR]', err.message)
  res.status(500).json({
    success: false,
    data: null,
    error: process.env.NODE_ENV === 'development' ? err.message : 'Server error'
  })
})
```

## 🔄 Embedding Service Integration
```javascript
import axios from 'axios'

const EMBEDDING_SERVICE = process.env.EMBEDDING_SERVICE_URL || 'http://localhost:5000'

export const getEmbedding = async (text) => {
  try {
    const res = await axios.post(`${EMBEDDING_SERVICE}/embed`, { text })
    return res.data.embedding
  } catch (error) {
    console.error('Embedding service error:', error.message)
    throw error
  }
}
```